questions.question:
How many times will this loop run?

```php
$i = 5;
while ($i > 0) {
    echo $i;
    $i--;
}
```

What is the output of this code?

```php
for ($i = 0; $i < 3; $i++) {
    echo $i;
}
```

What will this code output?

```php
$nums = [1, 2, 3, 4];
foreach ($nums as $num) {
    if ($num == 3) {
        continue;
    }
    echo $num;
}
```

How many times will this loop run?

```php
$i = 0;
do {
    echo $i;
    $i++;
} while ($i < 0);
```

What will this code output?

```php
for ($i = 0; $i < 5; $i++) {
    if ($i == 2) {
        break;
    }
    echo $i;
}
```

What is the output of this code using foreach?

```php
$arr = ['a' => 1, 'b' => 2];
foreach ($arr as $key => $value) {
    echo "$key$value";
}
```

How many times will 'Hello' be printed?

```php
for ($i = 0; $i < 3; $i++) {
    for ($j = 0; $j < 2; $j++) {
        echo "Hello ";
    }
}
```

What is the output?

```php
$i = 1;
while ($i <= 3) {
    echo $i;
    $i++;
}
```

